text: Let's Go Native is a 1930 American musical comedy movie directed by Leo McCarey and starring Jack Oakie, Jeanette MacDonald, Kay Frqncis, Charles Sellon, Richard "Skeets" Gallagher, Eugene Pallette, Iris Adrian. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1930 comedy movies Category:1930 musical movies Category:American musical comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Leo McCarey Category:Paramount Pictures movies
